videos.headline: UNLV airs it out to take the lead
videos.description: UNLV QB Kenyon Oblad throws the deep ball to Randal Grimes for the 63-yard touchdown to put the Rebels up on Vanderbilt.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UNLV airs it out to take the lead) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: Magyar increases UNLV's lead on Vanderbilt
videos.description: UNLV has Vanderbilt on upset alert as Chad Magyar scores from 14 yards out to increase the Rebels' lead to 34-10.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Magyar increases UNLV's lead on Vanderbilt) 2019/10/12
